room_title: Escape room "Area 51" by Optimal Escape in Evansville
room_description:
You and your friends were camping near Groom Lake. You accidentally witnessed an unusual event with some lights, a UFO, and small people. Shortly after that some armed military men arrived and put you in the back of a military van. You remember nothing after that.
You wake up in a small room and realize you have been captured. You now understand that you have to escape before you are silenced for what you witnessed. You have one hour.
